# Circular Buffer â€“ Readers and Writers (Java)

This project implements a circular buffer in Java that solves the readers and writers
(producer-consumer) concurrency problem using classic monitor synchronization
with `synchronized`, `wait()`, and `notifyAll()`.

## Files
- `MyCircularBuffer.java`: Implements a thread-safe circular buffer.
- `MyCircularBufferTest.java`: Tests the buffer using multiple reader and writer threads.

